{"tid":1995823,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[高達求職實戰系列]履歷表CV上的3點應做和避免位,避開中伏區,你問我答","createTime":"2020-04-30T14:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T10:54:08.000Z","uid":343020,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93e6dd0aa7dde84742eb667b6740fcc2c597f352","tid":1995823,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>[求職實戰系列]履歷表CV上的3點Do(應做) and Don&rsquo;t(避免),避開中伏區</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aEweaG5GHtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaEweaG5GHtQ&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f47a1d76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aEweaG5GHtQ</a><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修〔搵下有冇啲可以幫大家有一技之長/移民加分既知識〕<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n有咩疑難都可以盡量係到問，答到盡答<br />\n<br />\n其他<br />\n[求職實戰系列]9個構成履歷表CV的部位,教你快速製作履歷表(Resume)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DeNvVY-YoFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDeNvVY-YoFw&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=3bbac6cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DeNvVY-YoFw</a><br />\n見工面試服裝心得分享(2020年基礎篇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oTHtN2mrYw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoTHtN2mrYw8&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=8010c2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oTHtN2mrYw8</a>"},{"pid":"8e60d32ec9fdd7c11b651d1205dd2e802ed7b7fa","tid":1995823,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n