31e554a5c7a8057ca77e120f41b0e237b6f8c6e6","tid":1995823,"uid":104077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d740dc82aeeeb554f8008c4138b3e2b63900c3","tid":1995823,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16330c4dc7baf9f342c32f3024e88d23a49221d0","tid":1995823,"uid":104077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"點睇CFA level 1 candidate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"同其他candidate比多一皮，pass or fail都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"見好多人報完名交寫LinkedIn <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"係? 係linkedin見唔係好多，但講真cfa又唔會保證d咩，平常心就好"},{"pid":"b6d4010cfcd87791238152dea03c067d54caf75f","tid":1995823,"uid":249242,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"Age 一定唔洗寫，地址都冇需要，但假如你in iBank想show off 下你住貝沙灣或且羅便臣道，都可以寫。marital status 唔應該寫，有冇interview 唔應該受有冇結婚，age影響，否則已經可能有discrimination。你寫咗我都會hide左佢先forward 比line manager。我哋剩係想佢地based on candidates experience and education 去做judgment 。(其實line manager 望下你幾時grad再加你有幾多年experience 就知你幾大，寫黎做乜撚野？)<br />\n<br />\nCFA 同CPA 擺落去professional qualifications，CRE冇性趣知，大公司自然會有aptitude test 比你。<br />\n<br />\nOverall 份CV好小學雞，我收到未必會㨂黎in，你個video 都係靠害多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已上所有野填application form 或且online application system另計。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 10年Bank HR experience , 已經做到可以in manager level position grade hiring 。（幫post, 唔係本人，唔好問我HR問題）"},{"pid":"deacf5a9ebc80fbd43c470294501e23bf1c6f866","tid":1995823,"uid":36968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"咪同依條垃圾推post <br />\ncv多過一頁都講多出<br />\n仲要寫咁多無謂野<br />\n依個時勢真係人人都諗住做youtuber搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}